    "Additionally, MPT models can be efficiently deployed using standard NLP 1 3 as chatbots, are already widely employed.",
    "Conversely, in decision-making processes, we may still be far from their widespread application (Fig. 2).The healthcare applications of LLMs primarily involve chatbots and interaction systems, clinical documentation, medical literature summarization, as well as diagnostic and clinical decision support.",
    "For chatbot use, a limitation arises from the length of the context.",
    "Current models struggle to handle increasingly longer contexts while maintaining a high level of reliability and predictability.",
    "With the advent of applications like ChatGPT and the first version of Bing Chat (recently updated and renamed as Copilot, Microsoft), users have noticed that the longer they use the model in a single conversation, the more inaccurate its responses become."
